Loops
======
	1.for loop
	2.while loop
	3.do while loop
	4.for-in loop 
							let persons ={
							name:"hari",
							age:20
							};

							for(let key in persons){
								console.log(key)-> name, age pring not value
								console.log(persons[key]) -> value print
							}


							let colors =['red','blue'];

							for(let color in colors){
								console.log(color) -> key only print like index 0,1,2
								console.log(colors[color]) value print
							}

							object and array iteration purpose use
							key value pair also use this 
